 Galvatron watched as Guiledart made his proposal. "I like the idea. That way 
our approach will be a complete surprise." A light switched on in his optic. 
His probe had found something. He had sent a probe a masquito bot to each 
enemy base to scope it otu. He looked at Darkfates base. "It seems the preds 
have some company. I see omunious Prime. When they are done with them they 
shall be weakened we should attack then. For now I wish to train. Do you have 
a training room wich may  alter gravational pull in that area."

--part1_d4.17122f1.27a0d951_boundary
